<section id="tools_goto_dn_dialog">
	<title>Go to DN dialog</title>
	<para>
		The Goto DN dialog is used find an entry in the DIT by its distinguished name. 
	</para>
	
	<para>
		To start the Go to DN dialog
		choose <emphasis role="strong">Go to DN...</emphasis> from context menu.
	</para>	
								
	<para>
		<screenshot>
			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata scale="50"
						fileref="images/tools_goto_dn_1.png" format="PNG" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</screenshot>	
	</para>
	
	<para>
		Enter the DN of the entry into the input field and press OK.
	</para>
</section>